      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/canada-telecom-shares-drop-on-bmo-notes-on-rogers-bce-quebecor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 BMO 资本市场公布加拿大电信行业前景黯淡后，BCE Inc. 股价跌至十多年来的最低点，罗杰斯通信公司 (Rogers Communications Inc.) 遭遇 2024 年最大跌幅。]]></description>
